  "explanation": [
    "This is a 0/0 form limit. Using L'Hopital's rule:",
    "Differentiate numerator: <katex>$\\sqrt{2}(-\\sin x)$</katex>.",
    "Differentiate denominator: <katex>$-\\csc^2 x$</katex>.",
    "Substitute <katex>$x = \\pi/4$</katex>:",
    "<katex>$\\frac{-\\sqrt{2}\\sin(\\pi/4)}{-\\csc^2(\\pi/4)} = \\frac{\\sqrt{2}(1/\\sqrt{2})}{(\\sqrt{2})^2} = \\frac{1}{2}$</katex>."
